				<div class="faq_q round"><a href="#">Q: Is this site formally connected to Yale Law School?</a></div>
				<div class="faq_a">A: No, this site has no such connection. It was made by a student for the free use of other students.</div>
				<div class="faq_q round"><a href="#">Q: Why should I sign up?</a></div>
				<div class="faq_a">A: If you sign up, you'll be given a course cart and a course calendar. That way, you can easily keep track of the courses you're most interested in and see how they fit into your calendar.</div>
		
				<div class="faq_q round"><a href="#">Q: How did you get all this data?</a></div>
				<div class="faq_a">A: This site has only scraped and organized that data which YLS already made publicly available. </div>
			
