				<div class="faq_q round"><a href="#">Q: What is ratings view?</a></div>
				<div class="faq_a">A: Ratings view lets you view and rank classes along three different meta-scores, as calculated by Reed Schuler. This provides another (and, we think, very useful) way of picking your classes. Details on these meta-scores are <a href=''>available here</a></div>

